data.description: Don't miss this opportunity with a bonus 9' x 14' ADU opportunity in the backyard. This home has been updated with new interior and exterior paint, newer roof, laminent and tile flooring, ceiling fans, new gutters, drainage for dog run, new garage door and opener, all new fencing, low maintence backyard with deck and cover and covered side yard sitting area.  The Shed has power and can be upgraded to an ADU.
